transpose_dgRMatrix <- function(inmat) {
  if(class(inmat) != 'dgRMatrix')
    stop('inmat is not of class dgRMatrix')
  out <- new('dgCMatrix',
             i=inmat@j,
             p=inmat@p,
             x=inmat@x,
             Dim=rev(inmat@Dim),
             Dimnames=rev(inmat@Dimnames)
  )
  out
}
